int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|start
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|add_bar_int|0|1
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|add_bar_int|0|2
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|add_bar_int|0|3
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|add_bar_int|0|4
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|add_bar_int|0|5
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_sent_count|0
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|stop
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_sent_count|1
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|type|4
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|min|1
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|max|5
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|mean|3
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|first|1
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|last|5
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|count|5
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_field|0|status|1
int_bar_basic_aggregation_flushes_on_stop|expect_bar_open_close_aligned|0|3600000

